In[37]:
column_name = 'EngagementLevel'
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))

plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
sns.countplot(y=column_name, data=df, palette='Set3', hue=column_name, legend=False)  
plt.title(f' {column_name}')

ax = plt.gca()
for p in ax.patches:
    ax.annotate(f'{int(p.get_width())}', (p.get_width(), p.get_y() + p.get_height() / 2), 
                ha='center', va='center', xytext=(10, 0), textcoords='offset points')

sns.despine(left=True, bottom=True)

plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
df[column_name].value_counts().plot.pie(autopct='%1.1f%%', colors=sns.color_palette('Set3'), startangle=90, explode=[0.05]*df[column_name].nunique())
plt.title(f'  {column_name}')
plt.ylabel('')  

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
